@startuml archive-plan-precheck-decision

title archive_plan — retired decision boundary

start

:SDK agent needs to close out plan-shaped work;
:Check Agent Deck MCP registry;

if (archive_plan is registered?) then (no)
  :Use the active project or skill closeout workflow;
  :Preserve or record code changes according to that workflow;
  if (worktree cleanup is needed?) then (yes)
    :Call exit_worktree(worktreePath?, discardChanges?, deleteBranch?);
  else (no)
    :Leave filesystem state as the project workflow requires;
  endif
else (yes)
  :Not a current Agent Deck path;
endif

stop

note right
  Plan files, changelog indexes, review records, and archive directories
  are project assets. They are not Agent Deck MCP invariants.
end note

@enduml
